<br>
If I am really chain petting somewhere hard and saving all the mana I can, I just pull with and/or mix in 5hp of damage from the tradeskilled ceramic band that mages can click from inventory. 3 seconds cast time.<br>
<br>
I think Flame Shield damage doesn't count for anybody's damage. It definitely isn't going to give you full exp on a mob by itself.  You have to do direct damage to the mob.<br>
<br>
If the pet does all the damage credited on a mob, then you basically get diddly squat for experience, as compared to what you would get if you did 1hp of damage. I'm not sure of the percentage, but I wouldn't even consider it since just 1hp of damage nets you full exp.<br>
